 '["senior","elderly","old age","maintenance","parents","policy"]', true, now(), '[]'),
('National Food Security Act 2013', 'food-security-act-2013', 'Food',
 'The NFSA guarantees food security to 75% rural and 50% urban households with subsidized grains.',
